{"EpubVersion":2,"filepath":"","fixparentnode":"","floatingtheme":[],"folded":false,"markups":[{"date":"2025-03-18 11:11:55","docid":0,"id":2,"linecolor":"ffaa0000","linewidth":12,"originaltext":"徐珙出使安南，“天恩”、“正朔”，所表明的是一种天朝上国的心态。","page":0,"rect":[425.813718163154,321.77706918491316,716.3670465140988,358.6835232570494],"type":11,"uuid":"1c7363641c552a617b99c2ede24626c1"},{"date":"2025-03-18 11:14:48","docid":0,"id":4,"linecolor":"ffaa0000","linewidth":10,"originaltext":"中越之间地理上的阻隔，使得二者成为不同的政治单元。这一点在中国使臣诗歌中也得到了确认。","page":0,"rect":[45.57357632232675,478.29238180704544,209.9939762660237,546.9622375583791],"type":11,"uuid":"62a699351cead2b153d7d6012a1968bf"},{"date":"2025-03-18 11:17:02","docid":0,"id":6,"linecolor":"ffaa0000","linewidth":10,"originaltext":"对于中国使臣来说，两国之间的关系就像是周天子和诸侯。","page":0,"rect":[226.0265249925498,533.9934195343335,444.7669451992221,562.6137688205923],"type":11,"uuid":"141a5b16a9ef19d6b839da5237ecaa82"},{"date":"2025-03-18 11:21:25","docid":0,"id":8,"linecolor":"ffaa0000","linewidth":10,"originaltext":"中国的使臣观察到安南在风俗上有中国有所差异，并且刻意求异的心理，但基于“天朝上国”和华夏优越感而认为这是一种自甘为“夷”。","page":1,"rect":[556.5500381181116,132.11733741927048,693.8104279303209,242.21771709999211],"type":11,"uuid":"87f3db1208b46cf20e607ddf4de5a1f1"},{"date":"2025-03-18 13:11:36","docid":0,"id":10,"linecolor":"ffaa0000","linewidth":10,"originaltext":"这一部分谈的是明代安南男女的发型，不束发，男女一样。其王只有中国使臣来时才会束发。（从这里我们这可以清楚地看到安南地方不论男女的发型，和中国都存在着很大的差异。只有中国使臣来的时候束发，则是说明了他们在意中国使臣的看法）。同时，作者在这里也提到了染黑齿、赤足两个习俗。对于染黑齿，作者略有轻蔑之意。染黑齿之事，中国人赴越游记多有提及，此不赘述。赤足之事，蔡钧在<出洋琐记>（《晚清海外笔记选》第15页提到）。席地而坐，裸身操舟，屋舍简陋（《晚清海外笔记选》第17页提到）。","page":1,"rect":[97.13156165667621,51.55798533434947,234.3919514688855,435.0998229490316],"type":11,"uuid":"4079aeda5ec46baa169f326025d5f397"},{"date":"2025-03-18 13:21:58","docid":0,"id":13,"linecolor":"ffaa0000","linewidth":10,"originaltext":"作者在这里提到吃槟榔，喝椰汁的习俗。","page":1,"rect":[556.5500381181116,260.0916224456022,680.4605924419625,294.2360415891126],"type":11,"uuid":"cac8b2dfdac463ae8cc4b479019a3933"},{"date":"2025-03-18 13:24:18","docid":0,"id":15,"linecolor":"ffaa0000","linewidth":10,"originaltext":"在心态上，明朝使臣将安南视为夷。","page":1,"rect":[545.0415592488372,343.41300945914907,682.3019490610465,377.55742860265946],"type":11,"uuid":"f647ca6511cddc923ff604741d1f3c5a"},{"date":"2025-03-18 13:27:09","docid":0,"id":17,"linecolor":"ffaa0000","linewidth":8,"originaltext":"明代使臣出使安南，看到其宫中有舞蛇表演。中原宫廷文化中极少有舞蛇表演的记载，这一习俗有着印度文化的影子。","page":1,"rect":[239.3763604809082,358.6042015665913,537.7554544629595,389.52624662670485],"type":11,"uuid":"03b78fba47abac5c23be64eea858e9ac"}],"maxid":17,"notelinks":[],"summaries":[],"title":"徐珙出使安南","unimportant":[{"date":"2025-03-18 11:11:04","docid":0,"id":1,"imgfile":"5d9e861f3041521b06c821b6b73278e0.png","linecolor":"ffaa0000","linestyle":1,"linewidth":4,"page":0,"rect":[226.48686414732083,386.68489000762094,412.92422182956665,387.6055683171629],"type":1,"uuid":"3170300454822d41e87f9a208b0a91d2"},{"date":"2025-03-18 11:13:23","docid":0,"id":3,"imgfile":"3e4fb126b6a908beeea307dcd5a4f1c0.png","linecolor":"ffaa0000","linestyle":1,"linewidth":4,"page":0,"rect":[232.93161231411452,493.94391306925866,288.1723108866318,494.8645913788006],"type":1,"uuid":"00ede93e363dd353633593fbcafbb701"},{"date":"2025-03-18 11:15:47","docid":0,"id":5,"imgfile":"0a36ec45ca4bcfeddc85531d5a741147.png","linecolor":"ffaa0000","linestyle":1,"linewidth":4,"page":0,"rect":[229.7092382307177,519.2625665816624,360.9058973404462,519.7229057364334],"type":1,"uuid":"ca6df20a98c629d8c81bc53f869d7ac3"},{"date":"2025-03-18 11:18:52","docid":0,"id":7,"imgfile":"78bc309ee1f2e48151ad672d60316a9c.png","linecolor":"ffaa0000","linestyle":1,"linewidth":4,"page":1,"rect":[257.3295875169763,140.86378135991905,519.7229057364334,142.70513797900296,412.4638826747957,122.45021516907997,542.2795243202113,125.67258925247681],"type":1,"uuid":"a87df5c8c4006bf4bf18961d91b66953"},{"date":"2025-03-18 13:09:22","docid":0,"id":9,"imgfile":"e40dd4864e4f4e66ada12fc901a0a007.png","linecolor":"ffaa0000","linestyle":1,